GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SEC RETARIAT
New Delhi, the 29th October, 1954.
The undersigned is directed to inform all Mambers
of the Council of Ministers that the Prime Minister has
directed that Dr. Panjabrao Shamr ao Deshmukh, Minister of
Agriculture should take over charge of the Ministry of
Food & Agriculture till other arrangements are made after
his return to India.
(A. S. Cill)
for Secretary to the Cabinet.
To
All Members of the Council of Mnisters.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/
the Private Secretary to the Vice-President/t he Special
Assistant to the Prime Minister/the Principal Private
Secretary to the Prime Minister, for information,
ASGu
(A.S. Gill)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet,
Copy forwarded to-
All Ministries of the Government of India,
De partment of Parliamentary Affairs.
Secretariat of the Planning Commission.
Community Projects Administration.
ASCill
(A. S. Gill)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
"KSG"
